                    <div class="item">
                        <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/0/0f/D.C._eclipsed_in_hybrid_solar_event_%2810696089826%29.jpg" alt="Hybrid Solar Eclipse" style="height:400px; width:100%;">
