                    <div id="sunFactText">
                        For a long time up until the 16th century it was widely regarded that Earth was the center of the Solar System until the Polish astronomer Nicolai Copernicus wrote a model that described why the Sun must be the center of our Solar System. [<a href="https://www.pas.rochester.edu/~blackman/ast104/copernican9.html">REF</a>]<br>
